articles.author: Mairead McArdle, Mairead McArdle
articles.title: Coronavirus Kills Adviser to Iran’s Supreme Leader
articles.description: An adviser to Iranian Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei has died after he was infected with the coronavirus, which has infected several other top Iranian officials as well.

articles.author: Zachary Evans, Zachary Evans
articles.title: Health Officials Report Four New Coronavirus Deaths in Washington State, Bringing Death Toll to Six
articles.description: Officials in Washington State have confirmed four new deaths from Wuhan coronavirus in King County, bringing the state's death toll to six.

articles.author: Tobias Hoonhout, Tobias Hoonhout
articles.title: Cuomo Reveals First NYC Coronavirus Patient Is a Health Care Worker
articles.description: Andrew Cuomo revealed Monday that the first person to test positive for coronavirus in New York city was a health worker who had traveled to Iran.

articles.author: Jim Geraghty, Jim Geraghty
articles.title: The Coronavirus Is Dramatic Enough As Is, Thank You
articles.description: The coronavirus is really serious, and thus, it doesn’t really need any extra hype or drama.

articles.author: Rich Lowry, Rich Lowry
articles.title: What Should We Conclude from the Silent Spread of Coronavirus?
articles.description: An interesting piece at Slate argues that it is an encouraging sign that the effects of the disease are usually fairly mild.
